sequenceDiagram
    participant SQS as SQS Queue
    participant W1 as Worker (crashes)
    participant ECS as ECS Service
    participant W2 as Worker (replacement)
    participant DDB as DynamoDB

    W1->>DDB: SET status=PROCESSING
    W1->>W1: Printing...
    W1-xW1: CRASH (task killed)
    Note over SQS: Message invisible for 60s
    ECS->>W2: Launch replacement task
    Note over SQS: Visibility timeout expires
    W2->>SQS: ReceiveMessage (receiveCount=2)
    W2->>DDB: Check status = PROCESSING (stuck)
    W2->>W2: Re-process (crash recovery)
    W2->>DDB: SET status=DONE
    W2->>SQS: DeleteMessage
